auroraftp (1.0.0-3) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix lintian warnings and improve packaging quality
  * Add missing pyproject.toml build dependencies (python3-hatchling, pybuild-plugin-pyproject)
  * Add upstream metadata file for better package information
  * Fix debian/watch to check for OpenPGP signatures
  * Add DEB_BUILD_OPTIONS support for test skipping
  * Fix long line in build script for lintian compliance
  * Update author information in pyproject.toml

