auroraftp (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release of AuroraFTP (Closes: #1112136)
  * Modern FTP/SFTP client with PyQt6 GUI
  * Support for FTP, FTPS, and SFTP protocols
  * Secure credential storage using system keyring
  * Dual-pane file browser interface
  * Multi-threaded transfer queue with progress tracking
  * Site manager for connection profiles
  * Folder synchronization capabilities
  * Professional packaging with AppImage and .deb distributions

 -- Robert Clouthier <clouthierrobert@gmail.com>  Mon, 26 Aug 2025 12:00:00 +0000
